&lt;p>To demonstrate this, let&amp;rsquo;s run the following command:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code">
&lt;div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-powershell" data-lang="powershell">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="err">â¯&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">kubectl&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="py">exe&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">get&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">pods&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">-l&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">app&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">nginx&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">-n&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">default&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">-&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">-show-labels&lt;/span>
